examples.en: The weeds have overgrown the garden.
He acts like an overgrown child.
Stop acting like an overgrown child.
Their imagination is overgrown by fear.
Stop acting like an overgrown schoolboy.
The garden will be overgrown with weeds by the time we get back.
Even Professor Adams looked like an overgrown schoolboy beside him.
A few overgrown ruins are all that remain of that once mighty but now extinct civilization.
